<T>__{dissolve to:}
<A>__{later. the bar crowd has thinned. both mumford and skip have had a few. in fact, mumford is now carefully pouring them each another drink from a bottle of glensomething on the table.}
<C>__{mumford}
<D>__{you want me... to be... your friend.}
<A>__{skip beams. mumford leans forward in the same confidential way skip did before; he indicates that skip should lean in too. mumford is almost whispering }
