<D>__{but that's not what's really going on...}
<P>__{(skip is excited)}
<D>__{...what's really going on is... you have some problems and you want some therapy, but you feel it could be very bad for panda modem stock if word got out that you were having head problems.}
<A>__{skip confirms that's it.}
